---
const renderedAt = new Date().toISOString();
---
<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
	<meta charset="utf-8" />
	<title>SSR page</title>
</head>
<body>
	<h1>Server-rendered</h1>
	<p>Rendered at: <code>{renderedAt}</code></p>
	<p>Reload — the timestamp should change each time. If you see the same value twice or a 500, the Node runtime isn't executing.</p>
</body>
</html>
